responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "922B75C74FBE35BB35476D9EB738A6DD", "Dear Ida, I shall be away for a spell. I hired some swords to go Mungle hunting. Please keep the post tidy and open up if all is clear. Don\'t be alarmed if \"Ironboot\" is missing from the shed. I had to use it to ferry this lazy lot.")
name: MIDD_0020_CTK_MaidsNote_3
